latestIgtvVideos.title: Stepping as a showstopper 🦚
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Yesterday was a lot of fun. Meeting up with old friends, getting a feel for the stage, and being recognised by the organiser and team as the show-stopper. It had been a fantastic day for me. It has been a joy to meet you all. Everyone is extremely beautiful and elegant. It's a proud time for me because this is where I began my modelling career two years ago. And only yesterday, I was a show-stopper on the same stage.
My unexpected speech has caught me off guard. I get apprehensive about what to say, despite the fact that I have spoken my true feelings. Thank you to everyone.#yesterdaynight #showstopper #modelling
